Download and install VSCode


create a html file

Vscode shortcuts
================
1.   !              HTML 5 STRUCTURE
2.  img              image tag
3.  button*2         creates 2 buttons
4.  button.btn.btn-success{Success Button}
5.  table>tbody>tr*20>td*5{Data-$}    Table with 20 rows, 5 cols


to open the html file in browser
================================
1. install vscode extension - 
   a. open in browser (alt+b  /  alt+shift+b)
   b. live server

HTML - content of a webpage
CSS - for styling
Bootstrap - Responsiveness + pre-defined components-table,carousel,modal,card
Javascript - behaviour of a webpage